OL,5, The government has warned energy firms 
OL,6, not to hike direct debit payments for  
OL,7, customers who are making "huge efforts"
OL,8, to cut usage.                          
OL,10,FThe business secretary has written to  
OL,11,Fsuppliers asking them to ensure bills  
OL,12,Freflect what homes are actually using, 
OL,13,Fand do not over-estimate charges.      
OL,15,FGrant Shapps said he was concerned by  
OL,16,Freports that bills were rising despite 
OL,17,Fpeople cutting back on energy use.     
OL,19,FRegulator Ofgem has been asked to look 
OL,20,Fat making billing "more responsive".   
